Kadeem Hardison https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kadeem_Hardison 0 Kadeem Hardison (born July 24, 1965) is an American actor and director. He is best known for his role Dwayne Wayne on A Different World, a spin-off of the long-running NBC sitcom The Cosby Show. He also starred in the Disney Channel series K.C. Undercover as Craig Cooper, the title character's father. Kadeem_Hardison ( born July_24_,_1965 ) is an_American_actor_and_director .
